                "title": "Light trapping designs for thin silicon solar cells based on photonic crystal and metallic diffractive grating structures",
                "year": 2009,
                "venue": "Photovoltaic Specialists Conference",
                "citation_count": 1,
                "reference_count": 10,
                "abstract": null,
                "authors": [
